headline: Does Mosaic’s 37% Rally Signal More Room After Fertilizer Price Surge?
summary: Thinking about what to do with Mosaic stock? You are not alone. Whether you already own shares or are contemplating a position, Mosaic has given investors more than a few reasons to pay attention. Over the past year, the stock has climbed 35.9%, while year-to-date gains stand at an impressive 37.1%. After a slight dip of 1.8% in the last week, it is still up 2.7% over the past month and a remarkable 99.6% over the last five years.
